data.title: History: Wipro Limited
data.meta_description: Wipro Limited.docx - Free download as Word Doc (.doc / .docx), PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read online for free. Wipro Limited is an Indian multinational IT company headquartered in Bangalore, India. It has 147,000 employees serving over 900 clients in 57 countries. Wipro is the third largest IT services company in India. In 2013, Wipro demerged its non-IT businesses into Wipro Enterprises Limited to focus on its core IT business. Wipro began as a vegetable oil company in 1945 and diversified into IT in the 1980s, becoming a global leader in IT services and consulting.
